{"tid":1305314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那網民：罷買寶礦力改買國產能量飲品","createTime":"2019-07-10T23:12:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T23:50:10.000Z","uid":42188,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d71af4b79da6276ef6a71d699f6bf34ef157a78f","tid":1305314,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T23:12:10.000Z","msg":"昨日網上流傳，無綫電視的其一個廣告客戶寶礦力水特在社交網站facebook專頁在回覆客戶信息中指，因應目前社會情況，公司由上周起已抽起在TVB的廣告，預料需要兩周處理。<br />\n<br />\n寶礦力水特此舉獲大批網民讚好，不過另一邊廂，內地網民則批評寶礦力水特的做法，聲稱要罷買寶礦力改買內地國產的能量飲品。而一直以來甚至少在網上談及《逃犯條例》的前特首梁振英亦發聲，晚上在facebook發表帖文，批評「寶礦力黑白不分」，他更呼籲全國消費者要全面抵制寶礦力。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">愛國就要用國貨，寶礦力是小日本的！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d86da25e7ecb4d12c96a2249b8e8a81da08148","tid":1305314,"uid":54364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T23:13:27.000Z","msg":"口裏說不<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81525c2a8f9e1b184fcf55c45acd80e2642c3fe3","tid":1305314,"uid":104165,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T23:14:23.000Z","msg":"佢地不嬲都飲國貨架啦<br />\n鬼有錢買寶礦力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dee9d2275f7ea4ef4fa07dbe6c32b0274707874","tid":1305314,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T23:14:50.000Z","msg":"唔守唔硬碰冇問題，但我唔撚明點解有人借機帶風向，話唔好再搞連儂牆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304714\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"207374add7f4a8ee0bc32